{"lastModified":1762338481498,"uri":"c::27074328118::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nLASTAVICA is a 49.00m / 160ft Motor Superyacht built in 2021. Sleeping 36 guests in 18 cabins and with a crew of 8. Cruising at 8.00 kn/ph.\n\nWith a length of 49 meters. 18 spacious air-conditioned cabins with private toilets can accommodate up to 36 guests onboard. Lounge bar (VIP salon), jacuzzi, spacious sun deck, reception, modern kitchen, restaurant, and hostess on board. This mini-cruise ship is built in 2021 and operates deluxe cruise tours in Croatia. Cabins are located on the lower and main decks and are a mix of Double or Twin berths. Lastavica is stylishly decorated with modern, spacious indoor and outdoor social areas for guests to relax, dine or drink. Up top, there is a spacious sundeck area with loungers and a hot tub. A swim platform at the rear of the boat allows guests to swim, snorkel or make use of the onboard water sports activities.","blueprint":{"name":"LASTAVICA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e1eefa0-50d7-11f0-9cd4-01a98f749d0e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e1097c0-50d7-11f0-9cd3-01a98f749d0e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e1dde30-50d7-11f0-9cd3-01a98f749d0e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e23f8b0-50d7-11f0-aab6-23fe4494e10d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e1ea180-50d7-11f0-9cd3-01a98f749d0e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e27a230-50d7-11f0-b963-fb952842b5b0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5d5dcf40-a90e-11ef-841c-a7cdd26b57cb::assets::1e241fc0-50d7-11f0-b963-fb952842b5b0/{imageVariant}","/